NAME
    Log::Log4perl::Appender::Gearman - Log appender for posting job to
    gearman

VERSION
    Version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
      # in your log4perl config:
      # log4perl.appender.GM          = Log::Log4perl::Appender::Gearman
      # log4perl.appender.GM.job_servers = 127.0.0.1:$port
      # log4perl.appender.GM.jobname = logme
      # log4perl.appender.GM.layout = Log::Log4perl::Layout::PatternLayout
      # log4perl.appender.GM.layout.ConversionPattern=%m

AUTHOR
    Chia-liang Kao, "<clkao at clkao.org>"

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests to
    "bug-log-log4perl-appender-gearman at rt.cpan.org", or through the web
    interface at
    <http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=Log-Log4perl-Appender-Ge
    arman>. I will be notified, and then you'll automatically be notified of
    progress on your bug as I make changes.

